name: Octoberist.GitHub.io
body:
### Welcome to Octoberist
I love tools.  Especially tools that help you achieve that goal of writing quality code without being brought down by the mundane, the automatable, the boilerplate of it all.  That's what Octoberist is here to do.  I'm sharing tools that I find helpful day-to-day and hope that you'll find them useful as well.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
